                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Editorial Note</hi>
                </head>
                <p>No official <gloss target="#t_NATO1">NATO</gloss> record of this meeting has been
                    found in Department of State files, and no list of participants is available.
                    Secretary of Defense <persName corresp="#p_LOVETTRA1">Lovett</persName>
                    presumably headed the United States Delegation at this meeting. The telegraphic
                    report printed <hi rend="italic">infra</hi> is the only record of the meeting
                    available to the editors.</p>
            </div>
        </body>
